These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, scientific, time-travel, action
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, mirinda, lemonade
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of techno##2
10. the person eating banana is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the fan of funk is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | romance | action    | time-travel |
| Beverage           | fanta | lemonade       | almond-milk | mirinda     |

