.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, dog, turtle, ferret
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, fuchsia, mauve, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who likes apricot is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the owner of the dog is the colombian##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Pet          | frog  | dog    | turtle     | ferret       |
| Color         | mauve | apricot | black   | fuchsia |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

