.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, bellflower, poppy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, handball, parkour
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the person who growsdahlia is the social-worker##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the writer##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Flower   | dahlia      | poppy   | amaryllis   | bellflower |
| Sport           | parkour         | sailing       | handball  | soccer       |

