.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, pink, orange, mauve
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
House: townhouse, craftsman, farmhouse, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person who likes coral is the person eating corn##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes pink is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the craftsman house##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the townhouse house##1
11. the person who likes orange is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | mauve       | orange   | coral   | pink   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| House      | palace | craftsman    | farmhouse  | townhouse |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

