.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, drama, zombie
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, grey, blood-red, ivory
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person watching zombie movies##2
 3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person who likes grey is the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who likes green##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre    | drama    | zombie      | scientific          | comedy    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Color     | ivory     | blood-red      | grey     | green |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

