House: victorian, colonial, palace, wooden
 1. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
 2. the victorian house is between the wooden house and the palace house##2
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the palace house is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the victorian house is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the victorian house##1
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

