4 different games are played: go, bridge, canasta, billiard
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking juice is the person playing go##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |
