.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, red, white, amber
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, domino, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
11. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Color      | white       | red | blood-red        | amber        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Game   | snooker     | monopoly        | canasta    | domino      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

